attr.title: Counter-Strike 1.6
attr.desc: Counter-Strike 1.6 running on Xash3D FWGS using cs16-client. Supports offline play with YaPB bots and limited LAN/online multiplayer. Requires legally obtained game data.
attr.inst: Copy your own Counter-Strike 1.6 cstrike folder and a Half-Life valve folder into the port directory. Do not overwrite existing port files. See README for details.
